Type: Package
Package: logrxaddin
Title: Addin for the 'logrx' Package
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Ben", "Straub", , "ben.x.straub@gsk.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This is an extension package to 'logrx', which is a log creation 
  program focused on Clinical Reporting within the Pharma Industry.  This package 
  enables a simple 'shiny-based' Add-in that provides a point and click interface 
  to produce a log for a single program.
